longBusinessSummary: Mojave Brands Inc. does not have significant operations. Previously, it was engaged in the manufacturing, processing, and sale of cannabis extracts. The company was formerly known as Mojave Jane Brands Inc. and changed its name to Mojave Brands Inc. in March 2020. Mojave Brands Inc. is based in Vancouver, Canada.
